VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT CURLOPT_SSL_VERIFYPEER\s*,\s*0|CURLOPT_SSL_VERIFYHOST\s*,\s*0
WHEN EXPR MISSING:test|development|staging
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects TLS verification disablement in C HTTP clients.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Freertos Insecure Transport/Cert Bypass Marker.
